issue.title: [CF 1195] Icons overlapping with another addon (elvui)
issue.body:
http://imgur.com/EuQ67ZM
Hello. Some ElvUI elements (player frame's mana value, party frame's buffs/debuffs) seem to have higher strata then TellMeWhen icons. I wasn't sure where to post it, but i'd appreciate any advice on hot to handle this without sacrificing any ad-dons functionality.


> Posted by CurseForge user Belamoor | Imported from CurseForge issue #1195 | Raw

comments.body:
move the TMW icons so that they are not overlapping. The icon groups can be moved anywhere on the screen while in configuration mode. (make sure you're not in combat too)


> Posted by CurseForge user Adrian_G2

You can change the strata of each group in its group settings


> Posted by CurseForge user Cybeloras
